<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>NVIDIA on roiwk</title><link>https://www.roiwk.cn/tags/nvidia/</link><description>Recent content in NVIDIA on roiwk</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 03 Sep 2022 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.roiwk.cn/tags/nvidia/rss.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>关于我选择Manjaro作为桌面系统 第二集 NVIDIA驱动</title><link>https://www.roiwk.cn/post/manjaro-for-me-of-two/</link><pubDate>Sat, 03 Sep 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.roiwk.cn/post/manjaro-for-me-of-two/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="关于我选择manjaro作为桌面系统-第二集-nvidia驱动">关于我选择Manjaro作为桌面系统 第二集 NVIDIA驱动&lt;/h1>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>系统已安装，默认环境也都够用了，现在开始安装N卡驱动。&lt;br>
显卡放着,不能让它不干活啊，生产队的驴都不敢这么歇着。&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;h2 id="推荐方法一-从manjaro存储库自动安装nvidia驱动">【推荐】方法一: 从Manjaro存储库自动安装Nvidia驱动&lt;/h2>
&lt;hr>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>自动检测系统，并安装适当的Nvidia驱动
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:2;-o-tab-size:2;tab-size:2;">&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>sudo mhwd -a pci nonfree &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">0300&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>重启系统
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:2;-o-tab-size:2;tab-size:2;">&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>sudo reboot
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>重启后，配置显卡
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:2;-o-tab-size:2;tab-size:2;">&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>nvidia-settings
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;p>官方库有支持就是简单直接，一步到位。&lt;strong>安装成功&lt;/strong>&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>